    div.legal-container
      h1 Flora Terms of Service
      p Last Updated: Mar 30, 2026
      
      p This agreement is between the User and Flora (the "Platform"). Flora is a community-focused application dedicated to fostering connections, friendships, and romantic relationships among individuals who share specific lifestyle values.
      
      h2 1. Eligibility and Core Values
      p To maintain the integrity of the Flora community, all users must meet the following eligibility requirements:
      ul
        li #[strong Age Requirement:] You must be at least 21 years of age to create an account or use the Platform.
        li #[strong Lifestyle Alignment:] Flora is a community for vegans and those who respect the vegan way of life. By using the app, you agree to uphold these values and interact respectfully within this specific community framework.
        li #[strong Identity Verification:] To ensure safety, all users must undergo ID verification via Didit. Flora maintains a policy of zero local storage for sensitive ID documents; verification is handled securely by the third-party provider to confirm your identity without Flora retaining copies of your legal ID files.
      
      h2 2. User Content and Image Permissions
      p We value your privacy and aim for transparency regarding the data you share with us.
      ul
        li #[strong Limited Image Access:] Flora only requests permission to view and store the specific images that you voluntarily select and upload to your profile.
        li #[strong Strict Scope:] The Platform does not access your entire photo library, camera roll, or any other media files not explicitly chosen by you for display on your profile.
        li #[strong Ownership:] You retain ownership of all intellectual property rights in the content you upload. By uploading, you grant Flora a limited license to host and display this content solely for the purpose of operating the Platform.
      
      h2 3. Data Privacy and Infrastructure
      p Flora utilizes a modern, decentralized tech stack to ensure your data is handled efficiently and securely.
      ul
        li #[strong Location Privacy:] Flora does not track or store your precise GPS coordinates. We only collect and store city and zip code information to facilitate local connections while protecting your exact location.
        li #[strong Database and Hosting:] Your profile data is managed via a Turso database and processed through Cloud Functions.
        li #[strong Media Storage:] All user-selected images and profile media are hosted using Cloudflare R2 buckets.
        li #[strong No Data Selling:] Flora does not sell your personal data to third parties.
        
      h2 4. User Conduct
      p Flora is committed to providing a safe and welcoming environment. All users are expected to adhere to a high standard of behavior.
      ul
        li #[strong Best Possible Behavior:] You agree to act with kindness and integrity.
        li #[strong Zero Tolerance for Harassment:] Harassment, bullying, hate speech, or any form of predatory behavior is strictly prohibited.
        li #[strong Enforcement:] Flora reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to suspend or terminate any account that violates these standards of conduct or the community values.
      
      h2 5. Purpose of the Platform
      p The Platform is designed to facilitate connections through three primary avenues:
      ol
        li #[strong Dating:] Finding romantic partners who share vegan values.
        li #[strong Friends:] Building a social network of like-minded individuals.
        li #[strong Events:] Organizing and discovering community gatherings, meetups, and local vegan-friendly activities.
        
      h2 6. Premium Memberships and Payments
      p Flora offers enhanced features through its premium membership tiers. By purchasing a membership, you agree to the following terms:
      
      table
        thead
          tr
            th Membership Tier
            th Price
            th Duration
        tbody
          tr
            td Monthly Premium
            td $2.99
            td Recurring Monthly
          tr
            td Lifetime Access
            td $15.99
            td One-time Payment
            
      ul
        li #[strong Renewal:] Monthly subscriptions will automatically renew at the end of the billing cycle unless canceled prior to the renewal date.
        li #[strong Cancellation:] You may cancel your monthly subscription at any time via your account settings; cancellation takes effect at the end of the current paid cycle.
        li #[strong Refund Policy:] All membership purchases are generally considered final once the premium features have been accessed or utilized.
        
      h2 7. Limitation of Liability
      p Flora provides a venue for connections but is not responsible for the actions of its users. You agree to maintain your own safety when meeting individuals from the Platform. To the fullest extent permitted by law, Flora shall not be liable for any unauthorized access to our servers or any loss of data resulting from third-party service outages.
      
